playlist_videos.title: NEW EPISODE! Robot Cleaner 🤖🧼 Talking Tom Shorts (S3 Episode 9)
playlist_videos.description:
🫧🧹 Cleaning the house has NEVER been this fun for the friends! Why? Because they're not doing it! 🤣

Talking Ben got SO fed up with his friends being messy that he's actually whipped up some electronic butlers to make the house clean and tidy! 👋🤖🧼 Not bad living with an inventor, huh? 🤓  

BUT WAIT! Has Ben remembered to build in an off-switch in case the cleaners get too...enthusiastic? 😬 Watch and see!

playlist_videos.title: Cowboy Ginger 🌙 Talking Tom Shorts (S3 Episode 8)
playlist_videos.description:
Yeehawwww! 🤠 Cowboy Ginger is here and he's ready for anything. He's no yellow belly coward. 💪 He's a rootin'-tootin' buckaroo!

But does Talking Ginger have what it takes to be a SPACE cowboy?! 🌌😮 Because that's where he's needed. Roy Rakoon is back to his sneaky tricks, except this time they're out of this world! Roy is trying to steal the moon and Ginger's the only one who's spotted the crime! 💥🌙

Can Ginger follow him into space and thwart the varmint's terrible plan?! 🤔 There's only one way to find out!

playlist_videos.title: BEST Basketball Player 🏀⛹️ Talking Tom Shorts (S3 Episode 7)
playlist_videos.description:
Basketball’s a great game, but it’s not really fair, is it? 🏀 It’s hard to slam dunk the ball when you’re small, as Talking Ginger knows only too well. 🤾

While Talking Tom, Talking Angela, Talking Hank, and Talking Becca can all fly through the air and effortlessly drop the ball through the hoop, 💨😎 poor Ginger can’t reach. And every time Ginger finds a way to get bigger air, Talking Ben says it’s against the rules.🚫

Is there a way to make the game fun for everyone, including Ginger? There’s a courtside seat reserved just for you, 🏟️ so hit play and let’s find out! ▶️

#TalkingTomShorts #sports #basketball

playlist_videos.title: A Big Snowman ⛄🏰 Talking Tom Shorts (S3 Episode 6)
playlist_videos.description:
What’s your favorite thing to do when it snows? ❄️ Build a SNOWMAN? ⛄ Or have a SNOWBALL fight? 🤾 Hmmm… well, this episode has both! 😀

When Roy the Rakoon decides he’s going to steal the epic shield from the friends’ giant super-snowman, 🦝🛡️ the situation soon escalates into full-blown snowball war! 😲
Tom and his friends have a fort and a supply of snowballs, 🏰 but Roy has his own army of robo-snowmen! 🤖⛄

Who will triumph in the ultimate snowball showdown!? Hit play to find out! 👉▶️

#TalkingTomShorts #Snowman #Winter

playlist_videos.title: Yard Sale 💰🏠 Talking Tom Shorts
playlist_videos.description:
A yard sale can be a great way to clear out some old stuff and make a bit of cash while you're at it. 💵 Or, if you’re a customer, they’re a great place to pick up a bargain. 🤑 But a good yard sale is based on trust and respect - two ideas Roy the Rakoon knows nothing about! 🦝😠

This time the rascally robber is using his powers of disguise to trick the friends into giving their stuff away for nothing. 😮 But they’re onto his scheme, and are about to turn the tables… 🤔😉

Hit play to find out how the friends catch the crook and get their stuff back! ▶️🕵️‍♀️

#TalkingTom #Cartoon #YardSale

playlist_videos.title: Ben Goes to Space 🚀🪐 Talking Tom Shorts (S3 Episode 5)
playlist_videos.description:
Hands up who wants to go to space! ✋🌌

It would be totally awesome to visit an alien planet, of course. 🪐 But did you know that there are places on our own planet that seem like they belong on some other world?😯 It’s true! And some of them are closer to home than you think. Which is exactly what first-time space explorer Talking Ben is about to find out! 🧑‍🚀😄

Alright brave space cadets, prepare for launch… 3… 2… 1… BLAST OFF!! 💥🚀

#TalkingTomShorts #TalkingBen #Space

playlist_videos.description:

Yard sales are supposed to be fun! After all, you never know what you're gonna find. 🤩🔎 But what happens when what you find is a sneaky scheme organised by none other than... Roy Rakoon! 🤯

He's back and he's using all sorts of disguises to scam the friends! 🥸👉😮 Boooooooo! Will they figure out what he's up to before it's too late?

playlist_videos.title: Tricky Traps for Roy - Talking Tom Shorts
playlist_videos.description:
Does your home have a security system? 🛡️ A burglar alarm? 🚨 Some sensor-activated lights, maybe? 💡

How about a handful of MARBLES on the floor? Or a BUCKET of water on a tripwire? A cake CATAPULT!? 🎂💥

Talking Tom’s anti-burglary set-up looks more like a collection of pranks than a watertight home protection system. 😂 And that means you can be sure that something’s going to go wrong… 🫣 and just as sure that it’ll be really, really funny when it does! 🤣

Tune in to find out who gets a bucket of water on his head, 🪣 and who gets a face full of cake. 🤬 Roy the Rakoon is in the neighbourhood, so maybe it’ll be him. 🦝 But maybe not… 😁

playlist_videos.title: 🧁 The Cupcake Dream & More 🍭😴 Talking Tom Shorts (S2 Episode 55)
playlist_videos.description:
Have you ever been woken up from an AMAZING dream? 😴💭 All you want to do is get back to sleep, right? But it’s never that easy… 😒

The exact same thing happened to Talking Hank when he dreamed of a GIANT cupcake. 🧁 Just as he was about to take his first bite too! 😋

Despite napping pretty much all day every day, Hank still seems to find himself at the center of the action when things get crazy at the Talking Tom & Friends house. 🏡 As you’ll see from this HILARIOUS compilation, sometimes he brings it on himself, and sometimes he’s just at the wrong place (usually on the toilet 🚽) at the wrong time!

So, just like Hank would do, grab some snacks, 🍿 stretch out on the couch, 🛋️ and hit play! ▶️

playlist_videos.title: ✈️ Pilot Hank & More 😳 Talking Tom Shorts (S2 Episode 53)
playlist_videos.description:
Friends are all set for a much-needed holiday! 🏝️ But there's just one BIG problem – Talking Hank is terrified of flying! 🛩️😬 Can he overcome his fear with the help of his friends or will he have to stay at home? 😞

From VR games to real-life simulations, friends are doing everything in their power to help him conquer his fear of flying! 🎮✈️ But just when they think they have it all figured out, things take an unexpected turn… 😅

Talking Hank finds himself in a wild ride, flying away into the sky, leaving them all in a dizzying panic. ☁️😱 Can he stay calm and take control of the situation? When his friends get in danger, will he step up to the plate and become an unlikely hero – a pilot?! 👨‍✈️

Buckle up, press ▶️ and see as the chaos unfolds!

playlist_videos.description:

Don't miss a minute. 😃 There are action-packed, laser-powered running adventures in Talking Tom Hero Dash and Talking Tom Gold Run to catch up on! ⚡🎮 And have you seen Hank the Beekeeper gets his chase on when Roy Rakoon DARES to steal his honey? 🍯🐝💨

Talking Tom is the strongest, fastest runner, 💪 but Roy the Rakoon is the dirtiest, sneakiest cheat. 😏 With Roy cheating over and over again, it’s not just Tom’s strength and speed being put to the test - it’s his patience too! 😮‍💨

playlist_videos.description:
Ready to feel the love this Valentine's Day?! 💕 Join your favorite friends for a Talking Tom Shorts marathon! 😍

Valentine's Day is all about celebrating love – in all its forms! ❤️ Have you got a friend you'd do absolutely anything for? 🤔 That's exactly how Talking Tom feels for Talking Angela. 🙌 He'd go into outer space to fetch her a star to make her smile, save her from a crazy awkward dance party, and even figure out how to fit ALL her suitcases in the car for their road trip... 🧳🤣 

And you know what? She feels exactly the same way! Watch as she takes care of him when he's hurt, rescues him from his mistakes, and loads more! 🥰 

Friendship for the win! Join in on all the fun in this EPIC 12-episode collection of Talking Tom Shorts. Or get in the spirit of Valentine's Day and feel the love using the links below. 👇

You should definitely check out my shorts, trailers, and gameplay videos featuring me and my friends. Also, keep up to date with my crazy thoughts and ideas via my video blog Talking Tom Brainfarts. You could try looking, but you won’t find a funnier guy anywhere else! Stick around!

Stay awesome guys,
Tom :)

It's the night before Lunar New Year and Talking Tom, Talking Angela, Talking Hank, Talking Ginger, and Talking Ben are ready to enjoy their big Reunion Dinner... ❤️ But where's Talking Becca? 🤔

playlist_videos.description:
Want to help Talking Tom and his friends plant trees and get rewards? 🤩🌳 Join the Earth Day fun in Talking Tom Gold Run! https://o7n.co/ttgr_g024_yt_description_en

🍃 The brand new Nature Reward Blast is now live! 🍃 But Grow & Go is only available for a limited time. ⌛ So run and collect the water droplets Tom and his friends need to grow a tree before it’s too late! 🏃💨 The world needs more trees! 🌎 

The more 💧 you collect, the more your tree will grow – and the more rewards you’ll unlock! 🌳👉🏆  How awesome is that?! And we’re going to help plant trees in real life too. We’re helping the awesome folks at One Tree Planted on their mission to plant trees all around the world. 🌱 Let’s be like Tom and his friends this Earth Day and run to help the environment! 🙌

Think you’ve got what it takes to grow your tree big and strong, and unlock Super Tom and Super Angela?! 🦸 Play Grow & Go in Talking Tom Gold Run before the event ends! Talking Tom Gold Run is available to download and play on all major platforms worldwide. 🎮

It’s time to grow and go, go, GO! 👉 https://o7n.co/ttgr_g024_yt_description_en

playlist_videos.title: Smile for the Camera! 📸😁 Talking Tom & Friends | Animated Cartoons
playlist_videos.description:
Things look big in photos when they’re close to the camera, right? 📷 And small when they’re far away… 🔭 don’t they? It’s just a trick of perspective. Or, is it? 🧐

Imagine you’re posing for a photo with a taller friend, 👨‍👧 and you take a step towards the camera so that you’ll look the same height in the photo. But after the photo’s taken, you’re actually taller FOR REAL! 😮 That’s EXACTLY what happens to the Pets! 🤯

Poor Gus ends up so tiny that he’s in danger of being squashed by a giant Squeak. 🐜🦶 Fortunately, Sugar knows how to keep things in perspective, 🦄 and with a few clever camera tricks, everything gets back to normal. Well, almost normal…🤣

playlist_details.title: Talking Tom Heroes: Join the Adventure!
playlist_details.description: We're Talking Tom Heroes and we're here to save the day – for good! Super friends and superheroes, together we can do anything. Watch and see!

playlist_videos.title: Talking Tom Heroes - Friendship is a Superpower (Episode 52)
playlist_videos.description:
The Dark Mentor has been unleashed! Filled with darkness, it starts to bleed the light and colour and joy from the world. Will anything, anyone, be able to stop it from destroying... Everything?

Talking Tom Heroes throw themselves in the path of the Dark Mentor, determined to do whatever it takes to stop its domination. But with their powers glitching, will they be up to the epic task? 

Just when the heroes need a hero, Talking Ginger arrives! Will this super boost be what they need to defeat the Dark Mentor once and for all? Will the team be able to turn the light of their friendship against the rising darkness? Will it be enough?

There’s only one way to find out… Watch and discover that friendship is a superpower. Perhaps the greatest one of all!

00:00 💪  Friendship is a Superpower
06:51 🚂  Robber on the Train!  (Episode 29)
11:31 🦖 Pancakes and Dinosaurs (Episode 42)
16:43 💩 Stinky Angela (Episode 43)
21:53 👥 The Shadows (Episode 26)
